        "title": "<p>NMJ Lovers | Charlotte and Olli</p>",
        "description": "<p>For this chapter of NMJ Lovers, we step into Charlotte and Olli’s story — one that began long before either of them could have known what it would become.</p><p>From meeting in high school to building a life together over 14 years, their relationship has been shaped by growing up side by side — through young love, parenthood and the quiet, everyday moments that matter most. What began as something innocent has evolved into a deep partnership, grounded in friendship, loyalty and a shared life they’ve created together.</p><p>A story of choosing one another, again and again.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
