    "800eebd7-962e-4fa6-bc5d-8b818a1ba455": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "template--16177341137065__800eebd7-962e-4fa6-bc5d-8b818a1ba455-image-1": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<p><strong>What is something that has surprised you about marriage – perhaps a misconception proven wrong, or an assumption proven right?</strong></p><p>We have been together for so long that in some ways we already felt like we were married! But what has surprised us is how much more love we have for each other if that is even possible! I would still choose Olli over and over and over again. I love seeing him as a dad and I love that he still manages to surprise me with random things such as creating restaurants at home with our kids and taking me on thoughtful dates.</p><p><strong>Oliver, we’d love to know why you chose NMJ to help create the perfect engagement ring for Charlotte. How was your experience and how did you end up with the design that you did?</strong></p><p>Charlotte had her eye on a ring from there for a while! I went in one day and worked with the designer on the sizing and the style of ring and then went from there. They were so helpful and really made the moment more exciting and special. I loved all the extra little touches they included with the ring as well. </p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p><strong>What is something that has surprised you about marriage – perhaps a misconception proven wrong, or an assumption proven right?</strong></p><p>We have been together for so long that in some ways we already felt like we were married! But what has surprised us is how much more love we have for each other if that is even possible! I would still choose Olli over and over and over again. I love seeing him as a dad and I love that he still manages to surprise me with random things such as creating restaurants at home with our kids and taking me on thoughtful dates.</p><p><strong>Oliver, we’d love to know why you chose NMJ to help create the perfect engagement ring for Charlotte. How was your experience and how did you end up with the design that you did?</strong></p><p>Charlotte had her eye on a ring from there for a while! I went in one day and worked with the designer on the sizing and the style of ring and then went from there. They were so helpful and really made the moment more exciting and special. I loved all the extra little touches they included with the ring as well. </p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
