    "content_list_QdVqEa": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "image_y43eJM": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<p><strong>What is one of your favourite moments from your special day?</strong></p><p>Olli - I love that we got engaged in both of our favourite places (Tuscany) and that our son took the perfect photo of the special moment. I told him a few days before that I would be giving mummy something super special and he had to keep it a secret. There were a few times when he almost told her, but he did so well on the day with the camera capturing the moment! </p><p><br/></p><p>Charlotte - My favourite moment was when Olli got down on one knee and said why he wanted to marry me! Having our son there as well to share in the moment and the happiness after was pure magic. We went out for dinner to a cute little Italian restaurant that was in our villa where we were staying and there was a band playing, we had seafood marinara, pizzas and a lamb shoulder and it was all around just the most special day.  </p><p><br/></p><p>Olli - My favourite moment of our wedding was when Charlotte and my kids walked in. I’ll never forget that! </p><p><br/></p><p>Charlotte - my favourite moment of our wedding was hearing Olli’s vows and seeing his face as I walked down the aisle. Such a beautiful moment, I definitely had to hold back the tears! </p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p><strong>What is one of your favourite moments from your special day?</strong></p><p>Olli - I love that we got engaged in both of our favourite places (Tuscany) and that our son took the perfect photo of the special moment. I told him a few days before that I would be giving mummy something super special and he had to keep it a secret. There were a few times when he almost told her, but he did so well on the day with the camera capturing the moment! </p><p><br/></p><p>Charlotte - My favourite moment was when Olli got down on one knee and said why he wanted to marry me! Having our son there as well to share in the moment and the happiness after was pure magic. We went out for dinner to a cute little Italian restaurant that was in our villa where we were staying and there was a band playing, we had seafood marinara, pizzas and a lamb shoulder and it was all around just the most special day.  </p><p><br/></p><p>Olli - My favourite moment of our wedding was when Charlotte and my kids walked in. I’ll never forget that! </p><p><br/></p><p>Charlotte - my favourite moment of our wedding was hearing Olli’s vows and seeing his face as I walked down the aisle. Such a beautiful moment, I definitely had to hold back the tears! </p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
